Saat ini, keluarganya sedang menghilang.

90
00:08:01,380 --> 00:08:02,160
Eh?

91
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:05,080
Kemungkinan keluarganya dijadikan sandera,

92
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,010
